text: Noor Muhammad Khan is a Jatiya Party (Ershad) politician and the former Member of Parliament of Tangail-6. ==Career== Khan was elected to parliament from Tangail-6 as a Bangladesh Nationalist Party candidate in 1979. Khan was elected to parliament from Tangail-6 as a Jatiya Party candidate in 1986 and 1988. ==References== Category:Jatiya Party politicians Category:Living people Category:2nd Jatiya Sangsad members Category:3rd Jatiya Sangsad members Category:4th Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
